      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKOTA COURTNEY (6) was below best at her last start when 7th at this track following a second place finish (23.30) there two back. Has good speed so she should be prominent despite the draw. Tough to beat if on-song. BIGBAD ESME (3) was sent out big odds last time but scored an upset win in a Grade 5 at Gosford (22.49). Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Must be included in calculations. MARVELLOUS DUNN (1) produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at Taree Super Track over 300m behind Weekend Scotch (18.42) in a Mix 2/3. Was in the money prior to that. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Should be about the money. IMPERATOR (8) placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.",
